javax.wsdl.extensions.ExtensibilityElement
public class JMSServerBehaviorPolicyType
extends TExtensibilityElementImpl

JMS configuration policy for Celtix Server. These are used for configuring JMS port on Celtix server side. Sets selection criteria for messages received by server
